subtitleNullable: A JKSE historical data from 1990 to 2022
descriptionNullable:
The historical data of Jakarta Stock Exchange Index from 1995 to 2021, based on the information taken from [Yahoo! Finance](https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EJKSE/history?p=%5EJKSE). The original dataset contain empty data from when the market was close. It create many rows of Null data. I clean them and adding two columns to show the year and quarter of year of each rows. I hope by doing that I can make time series analysis of this dataset easier.

The image source: [Sushobhan Badhai via Unsplash](https://unsplash.com/photos/LrPKL7jOldI).
